assets.description:
My first attempt at creating a character in GoogleVR’s Blocks tool - in this case, I wanted to create some kind of D&D style elemental. Something monstrous and powerful that could smash through enemies with ease.

Inspired obviously by a lot of fantasy literature, games, and movies. There are a few aspects of the model which I am not entirely happy with and would like to go back and revisit now that I am more familiar with the tool.

assets.name: assets/f2q3r-XbW1Q
assets.description:
Part 3 of 6
A critical hit!

Part 4: https://vr.google.com/objects/cstfYkow3DM?e=VrZandriaUiM1

I started to add the cave environment proper here. It blocks many viewpoints, but I didn't think of that when making it originally since I was standing within the cave. There is a wonderful sense of the feeling of action here with the fighter dodging under the swing, along with the power of the mace hitting the cave walls.
